| Folder             | Purpose                          |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------- |
| `src`              | All application code             |
| `models`           | Data models (`Document`, `Page`) |
| `reader`           | PDF reading logic                |
| `utils`            | Logging, exceptions, helpers     |
| `tests`            | Unit tests                       |
| `docs`             | Architecture, notes, diagrams    |
| `data/sample_pdfs` | Sample papers for testing        |
| `data/outputs`     | Exported TXT, JSON, Markdown     |
| `notebooks`        | Temporary experiments only       |
